content.text: At the end of the day, you want to see and be proud of what you have achieved? You love to contribute an important part to a successful project? Welcome to Die Schittigs.

We're looking for you:

As a Frontend Developer (m/f/d) you develop high-quality digital products with a great team.

What you do:

  • Implementing screen layouts in HTML/CSS
  • Developing web applications in JavaScript
  • Developing frontend templates with PHP
  • Developing concepts and evaluating complex websites and apps from a technical point of view

Your skills:

  • At least 3 years of experience in web development
  • Profound knowledge of HTML and CSS & Javascript
  • Knowledge of PHP
  • Strong UX design sensibility
  • Basic Git knowledge
  • Optional: Experience with ReactJS, Laravel or Contao
  • Team spirit
  • High standards – regarding the implementation of designs and regarding your code

What to expect:

  • Flexible working hours, no overtime
  • 30 vacation days
  • 2.5 minutes distance to the train station
  • We cook and lunch together almost every day
  • Friendly, appreciative atmosphere
  • Web developers are involved in the whole project: from offer, layout to support & care
